title: Don't Trend on Me 2/5: Meek Mill vs Nicki Minaj, Mayor Pete, Mitt Romney, Trayvon Martin, Robert Pattinson

description:
On this edition of Don't Trend on Me Jack and Miles discuss the Meek x Nicki beef happening right now on Twitter, Pete "passing" Bernie on the popular vote, Mitt Romney becoming the first to advocate for impeachment within party lines, Trayvon Martin would have been 25 today, and Robert Pattinson, not Jack, named the sexiest man in the World.
